{"tid":631504,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唱呢首歌，可能真係唱左你做兵既心聲","createTime":"2018-04-16T13:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T02:29:41.000Z","uid":132678,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f98381ffe749f0c693c41accb1a5ab2eeeda53","tid":631504,"uid":132678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T13:45:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N0czP7bWIdo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN0czP7bWIdo&d=jl9%2FGclZ4d7fMGeX%2F4pQhV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=103c1f68\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N0czP7bWIdo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n填詞：梁芷珊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;平日杯酒不沾　今晚總喝不厭&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n或者自己總會因為佢，最少都醉過一晚或更多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;我努力試探你　接受我的真心可以嗎&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n為左佢不斷去同佢傾計去了解佢，為既只係希望佢可以接受到自己對佢既心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;怎麼你眼裡只得他   我也不知道&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n諗極都唔明白點解佢會選擇左別人，可惜既係佢眼中既&quot;他&quot;唔會係自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;如今這算甚麼　你是否非他不嫁&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n好想問一句&quot;你係咪真係揀定左佢，希望佢係你最後一個伴侶？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;當選了是他　我認輸　都不可怕&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n知唔知其實當你選擇左佢，就算要我認輸，其實根本一點都唔可怕<br />\n反正我其實已經做不了什麼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;最怕其實被取消資格  還不知道　拚命掙扎&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n最可怕既係，原來自己在佢心目中什麼都不是，但自己卻不斷咁去付出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;如今這算甚麼　我是否這麼討厭&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n有時真係會問自己一句&quot;我係咪真係咁黑人憎呢？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;只知道付出　以後都不知怎算&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n最可笑既係，除左為佢付出之外，咩都唔識做，之後要點自處，亦都唔知道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">&quot;最怕其實是輸得很遠  還不知道　惹人生厭&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n或者最怕既一個事實就係，原來由始至終，自己都不值一提，更被你討厭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被取消資格的自己，卻只想為佢付出。。。<br />\n或者自己只係一隻兵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝各位做緊兵既巴絲，<br />\n早日脫離苦海，唔洗再做兵，<br />\n<br />\n將來既事冇人會知<br />\n可能到有一日,佢會明白你既真心<br />\n又或者<br />\n會遇到一個更懂得欣賞你自己既人，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位共勉之。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請多支持,如喜歡可訂閱YOUTUBE CAHNNEL及FACEBOOK PAGES 等等,多謝各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nYOUTUBE CHANNEL：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw&d=jl9%2FGclZ4d7fMGeX%2F4pQhV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=44b0a8a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw</a><br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MOONMANMUSIC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMOONMANMUSIC%2F&d=jl9%2FGclZ4d7fMGeX%2F4pQhV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b4b0cf69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MOONMANMUSIC/</a><br />\n<br />\nEMAIL：<br />\nmoonmanmusic01@gmail.com"},{"pid":"9e709973b0aa42d74e6923d869c0a713471758f6","tid":631504,"uid":132678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a465670557a47d91d6b556c8a408c525a5d9cf","tid":631504,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c56bf4ae03ce0cca45491e4b8cc2d560f5c770ef","tid":631504,"uid":132678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f5a465670557a47d91d6b556c8a408c525a5d9cf","tid":631504,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"你又出現啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" cl